descp2: A `tf.TensorShape` or `tf.int64` vector tensor-like object representing the equivalent dense shape of a row in the resulting`tf.SparseTensor`. Each element of this dataset must have the same rank as`row_shape`, and must have size less than or equal to `row_shape` in each dimension.
